# API Tests

## Get All Menu Items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems


### Create a New Menu Item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fries",
  "price": "3.99",
  "description": "Fresh fries!",
  "image": "images/fries.jpg"
}

### Update a Menu Item
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mac & Cheese",
  "price": "9.99",
  "description": "Creamy cheddar cheese mixed with perfectly cooked macaroni, topped with crispy breadcrumbs. A classic comfort food.",
  "image": "images/mac-and-cheese.jpg"
}

### Delete a Menu Item
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems/1

### Retrieve a Non-Existing Menu Item
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems/25
